<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%- title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script defer type="text/javascript" src="../../public/js/auctionProductDetail.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/css/auctionProductDetail.css">
</head>
<body>

  <div id="auction_product"></div>
  <div id="countdown"></div>

  <div id="purchase_btn"></div>
  <button id="btn2" class="openBtnBid">입찰하기</button>

  <div class="modalBid hiddenBid">
    <div class="bgBid"></div>
    <div class="modalBoxBid">
      <p>※ 금액은 5,000원 단위로만 입찰 가능합니다.</p>
      <p>입찰 가격: <input type="text" id="bid_price">원</p>
      <button class="modal_button" type="button" onclick="bidBtn()">입찰하기</button>
      <button class="closeBtnBid">취소</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <button class="openBtn">상품신고</button>

  <div class="modal hidden">
    <div class="bg"></div>
    <div class="modalBox">
      신고 제목:
      <SELECT NAME=sltSample SIZE=1 id="report_title">
        <OPTION VALUE='불친절한 대응' SELECTED>불친절한 대응</OPTION>
        <OPTION VALUE='불량 상품 판매'>불량 상품 판매</OPTION>
        <OPTION VALUE='규정위반 상품'>규정위반 상품</OPTION>
        <OPTION VALUE='기타'>기타</OPTION>
      </SELECT>
      <p>신고 내용: <input type="text" id="report_content"></p>
      <button class="modal_button" type="button" onclick="reportBtn()">신고하기</button>
      <button class="closeBtn">취소</button>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>